----- lved=================================================================================================The Tlc configuration file ends here.---tla+utils  This is a simple example, and you would need to adjust it according your needs (e.g., the values for `Jug` or `DieHarMaj`). The module names like DieHarder represent an old problem of die hard which has been extended in this manner with new parameters(Goal , Jug etc.).
